OL,3,CProgramme listings for
OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 11 MAY
OL,4,G2000FLost Cities of the Ancients
OL,5,     GDocumentary series on lost
OL,6,     Gcivilisations. The story of the
OL,7,     Gformidable Hittite empire and the
OL,8,     Grediscovery of their astonishing
OL,9,     Gcapital, Hattusha.
OL,10,G2100FArt of Scandinavia
OL,11,     GAndrew Graham-Dixon explores the
OL,12,     Gextraordinary art to come out of
OL,13,     Gthe dark Norwegian soul, most
OL,14,     Gfamous for producing The Scream
OL,15,     Gby Edvard Munch.
OL,16,G2200FThe Sky at Night
OL,17,     GThe team explore the remarkable
OL,18,     Gstory of Jodrell Bank Observatory
OL,19,     Gand its towering Lovell
OL,20,     GTelescope, which scientists have
OL,21,     Gused to listen to the cosmos for
OL,22,     Galmost 70 years.
